The UC Office of the President Public Records Act (CPRA) office continues to collect and review voluminous records responsive to your recent CPRA request. Attached is the first batch of 849 pages of responsive records found in a search of President Drake's emails. Please note that student names and identifying information was redacted pursuant to FERPA, and private email addresses/phone numbers were redacted for privacy purposes.

